@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@email =ashishlukka2005@gmail.com
@password =ashish@12345
@token = PASTE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@clientObjectId = PASTE_CLIENT_OBJECT_ID_HERE
@clientRouteId = PASTE_CLIENT_OBJECT_ID_HERE
@recommendationId = PASTE_RECOMMENDATION_ID_HERE

### Velocis NBA Demo Setup
# 1. Inject the following MongoDB objects directly in Compass or mongosh.
# 2. After injection, use the HTTP requests below in order.
# 3. Replace placeholder ids before running the later requests.

### MongoDB objects to inject: existing CSM user reference
# Use the existing CsmUser for:
# email: ashishlukka2005@gmail.com
#
# Copy that user's _id from MongoDB and paste it into the client object below as csm_owner.

